high_descs: Make a left, a right to walk through to the next room, all the way to the other side to reach the TV set.
Pick up the credit card from the TV console.
Walk towards the lamp right next to the TV set.
anns.task_desc: Look at a credit card under a tall lit lamp.

high_descs: walk through living room to face tv and tv stand
pick up blue credit card from left side of tv stand
walk slightly right to face floor lamp
anns.task_desc: turn on floor lamp while holding credit card

high_descs: Turn and go in the other room to the tv.
Pick up the credit card that in on the left corner of the tv stand.
With the credit card in hand turn around and go behind the two chairs that are on your left.  Go to the lamp behind the chairs.
While holding the credit card in one hand turn the light on with the other so you can look at the credit card.
anns.task_desc: Take credit card to light to look at it.
